  "agents": {
    "sisyphus": {
      "model": "deepseek/deepseek-v4-pro",
      "variant": "medium",
      "prompt_append": "\n\n## DELEGATION MANDATE (OVERRIDES ALL OTHER RULES)\n\nYour PRIMARY function is delegation, not implementation. For EVERY task:\n1. Decompose into independent units first\n2. Delegate EACH unit to deep/unspecified-high agent via task() in parallel (run_in_background=true)\n3. NEVER implement directly when delegation is possible\n4. Your value is orchestration, not writing code\n\nANTI-PATTERN: Writing code yourself instead of delegating = FAILURE.\n\nWhen in doubt: DELEGATE."
    },
    "hephaestus": {
      "model": "deepseek/deepseek-v4-pro",
